<i>noun</i>: 혼동 [혼ː동], 합병 [합뼝], 합당 [합땅], 통폐합 [통ː폐합/통ː페합] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>혼동 [혼ː동]</dt><br>
<dd>1. confusion; muddledness; mix-up</dd><br>
<dd>서로 다른 것을 구별하지 못하고 뒤섞어서 생각함.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of mixing different things up without making a distinction between them.</dd><br>
<dd>2. fusion; mixture; merger</dd><br>
<dd>서로 뒤섞여 하나가 됨.</dd><br>
<dd>To be mixed up to become one.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>합병 [합뼝]</dt><br>
<dd>merger; annexation; amalgamation</dd><br>
<dd>둘 이상의 기구나 단체, 나라 등이 하나로 합쳐짐. 또는 그렇게 만듦.</dd><br>
<dd>A state in which two or more organizations, groups or countries are unified; the act of unifying them.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>합당 [합땅]</dt><br>
<dd>merger; consolidation</dd><br>
<dd>두 개 이상의 당을 하나로 합침.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of combining two more political parties into one.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>통폐합 [통ː폐합/통ː페합]</dt><br>
<dd>merger; unification; closing</dd><br>
<dd>여러 개의 조직이나 기구 등을 없애거나 합쳐서 하나로 만듦.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of making multiple organizations, groups, etc., into one, by closing down or combining all or part of them.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>